{"tid":2107944,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"開唔到部機","createTime":"2020-07-14T08:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T19:09:19.000Z","uid":211823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"26f942b7fc28699aebb08e3c53f941e036b7cb56","tid":2107944,"uid":211823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"前幾日無聊想拆部機學下點砌<br />\n拆完之後裝返好哂所有嘢就出事<br />\n開咗機10-20秒就會自動熄機唔識著返<br />\n係咪太熱開唔到定點<br />\n明明拆前都仲好地地 求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSpec:<br />\nMb Asus H61M-K<br />\nRam1 Kingston KVR1333D3N9/4G x1<br />\nRam2 Kingston KVR13N9S8/4 x1<br />\nHdd Seagate Barracuda 500gb<br />\nCooler master gx 550w<br />\n粒cpu開唔到機睇 唔記得係咩sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n部機其實都好耐歷史 插細力啲<br />\n如果可以整得返都盡量唔想換哂所有嘢"},{"pid":"427dadb4fac759226a378a2e6736d65c3ec6e643","tid":2107944,"uid":211823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5nG7fo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5nG7fo.png&h=55c493fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"125ae3f7bb7df4cd56eb90eb6c9776d3893ba6af","tid":2107944,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"部牛唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf1ae93f358be76ce11d6fa550f6edec2319e79","tid":2107944,"uid":211823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"125ae3f7bb7df4cd56eb90eb6c9776d3893ba6af","tid":2107944,"uid":19005,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:27:25.000Z","msg":"部牛唔夠力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"但點解拆之前又夠力"},{"pid":"64d6f60ca16b9431ecad929994de2781c6367d78","tid":2107944,"uid":77973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"咩畫面